{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FilterOutputStreamRef\/writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Tries to write the bytes contained in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"nVectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vectors"},{"type":"text","text":" into the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream. Will block during the operation."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"writev","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GOutputVector","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"nVectors","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bytesWritten","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gsize","text":"gsize","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">! = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nVectors"},{"text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vectors"},{"text":" is 0, returns 0 and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"does nothing."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"nVectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in ","type":"text"},{"code":"vectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is 0).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancelled"},{"text":" will be returned. If an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"partial result will be returned, without an error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some implementations of "},{"code":"g_output_stream_writev()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" may have limitations on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregate buffer size, and will return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"text":" if these","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"are exceeded. For example, when writing to a local file on UNIX platforms,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the aggregate buffer size must not exceed ","type":"text"},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" bytes.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/filteroutputstreamref\/writev(vectors:nvectors:byteswritten:cancellable:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE6writev7vectors8nVectors12bytesWritten11cancellableSbSPySo14_GOutputVectorVGSg_SiSpySuGSgAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO21FilterOutputStreamRefV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"writev"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GOutputVector"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"text":"nVectors","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"bytesWritten"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"gsize","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gsize","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preci